15: Don't you know when to give up?!
27:
Aw... Are ya angry I tricked ya? But 
I was just having some fun!
Now, buh-bye!
37:
I'm Folus the Clown! One might call 
me a bon viveur.
39:
I was trying to follow those monsters 
out of the Kaleidoscope, but—ah-HAH
—you looked more fun!
41:
So I started making bets with myself.
Will he cut me, or will he not? Will he 
mourn me, or will he not?
47: Ya wanna bet on that? Teehee.
51:
Anyhoodle, what I wanna know is why 
DIDN'T ya cut me? What was stopping 
ya, buster?
58:
Is it 'cause I'm people-shaped?
Ah-HAH! But so are gingerbread men, 
and neither of us are human!
61: Is it 'cause I look like a giiiirl?
69:
Whoopsie! I see. You're the type that 
takes offense to that kinda stuff, huh?
72:
Well, my money says it's 'cause 
I laughed. Teeheehee! 'Cause that 
probably means I can talk and think 
and cry and sigh...
74:
But what if I hadn't? What if I'd stayed 
silent the whooole time. Maybe even 
bared my fangs a little?
77:
Would you have cut me then? Before 
even finding out if we could be friends?
81:
Wow, mister! You sure have a heart of 
gold!
89:
I mean, my questions turned you so 
dark and gloomy, you looked like 
a regular ol' storm cloud!
Hehe. I like YOU!
93:
Let's be pals, okay? Compadres! 
Bosom buddies!
97:
Huh? Uh, hold on. Give me some time 
to think...
104:
I just put a little curse on you. Ah-HAH! 
But don't worry. It works both ways!
106:
You get bewitched by me—hee-hee. 
And I go crazy over you!
114: I've never felt more scared in my life...
